### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Products - all (EN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Accept-Language: en

### Products - by type (IT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?type=footwear
Accept-Language: it

### Metadata fields - all types (EN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metadata-fields
Accept-Language: en

### Metadata fields - by type (IT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metadata-fields?type=electronics
Accept-Language: it

### Filters - by type (IT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products-filters?type=footwear
Accept-Language: it

### Filters - by type (EN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products-filters?langtype=electronics
Accept-Language: en

### Reindex products to Meilisearch
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reindex
Content-Type: application/json

